    {
        "content": "<p>The last command, the one defining <code>structA</code> is doing something very different from the <code>instance</code>.</p>\n<p>It defines a structure and it is tells Lean that when the user wants to create a new element of that structure, leaving out any field is allowed and that Lean can fill in <code>a</code> with <code>2</code>, <code>b</code> with <code>a</code> and <code>c</code> with <code>sorry</code>.</p>",
